  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to evaluate the effects of a video-supported group-based Otago
      exercise programme intervention on balance, mobility, physical performance and aerobic
      endurance in community-dwelling older adults 65+ years old.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
